{"tid":2274181,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"採訪「和你 Lunch 」被捕　浸大學生記者被控阻差辦公、拒捕","createTime":"2020-11-06T09:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T10:04:12.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d591f8691a54e87430dd59065d8fa77c649cd6d7","tid":2274181,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"今年 5 月 8 日，有市民在中環 ifc 商場「和你Lunch」，浸大學生記者鄧澤旻在採訪期間被捕，事隔半年遭警方正式落案起訴，控以阻差辦公及拒捕兩罪，今（ 6 日）在東區裁判法院提訊，准保釋至明年 1 月 8 日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n控方案情指，<span class=\"red\">案發時鄧揹著大背囊，行跡可疑</span>，與另一名男子同行。<br />\n<br />\n在搜袋期間，鄧不停尖叫，令大量市民包圍警方，部分人指罵警員「死黑警」、「做乜X」。<br />\n基於鄧的行為，警員決定為他鎖上手扣，但鄧非常用力地反抗，並舉起右手避免遭上手扣，使<span class=\"red\">四名警員需合力制服他</span>。<br />\n<br />\n控方案情提到，在制服鄧於地上時，一名警員曾用手掌心保護其前額，惟<span class=\"red\">鄧的鼻子亦受傷流血</span>。"},{"pid":"e6ad1c16bfc83c31d7bfce005eb24625abc39089","tid":2274181,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:14:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA-%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0-lunch-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC-%E6%8B%92%E6%8D%95-%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0-lunch-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E6%258B%2592%25E6%258D%2595-%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9gu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=c06e5bae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0-lunch-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25